    "description": "Cominix Co.,Ltd. operates as a specialized trading company in Japan and internationally. It operates through Cutting Tools Business, Wear-Resistant Tools Business, Overseas Business, Optical Products Business, E-commerce Business, Kamogawa Manufacturing Solutions (KMS) Business, and Other Businesses segments. The Cutting Tools Business segment sells cutting tools, work holding tools, precision measuring instruments, machine tools, and other products. The Wear-Resistant Tools Business segment sells canning tools and wear-resistant tools. The Overseas Business segment offers cutting tools, canning tools, wear-resistant tools, tool holders, precision measuring instruments, machine tools, mineral resources, etc. The Optical Products Business segment sells optical components, light source devices, optical fibers for lighting, etc. The E-commerce Business segment sells cutting tools and other products through internet and its e-commerce website. The KMS Business segment manufactures cutting tools, grinding wheels, and other products; and operates a renovation business that provides maintenance for tools, machine tools and equipment. The Other Businesses segment manufactures and sells cutting tools and other products. Cominix Co.,Ltd. was founded in 1945 and is headquartered in Osaka, Japan."
